title: Microsoft Windows XP Professional SR3 (Norwegian Volume License)
description:
Norwegian Volume Licence of Windows XP Pro (32-bit), pre-patched with Service Pack 3.


The following modifications have been done:

- License-key already entered.

- Windows Messenger removed.

- System Restore disabled.

- IIS disabled.

- Data Execution Prevention set to OptIn.


The following drivers are included:

- nForce v6.86 drivers included (only installed if you have the hardware).
 - Audio driver
 - Ethernet driver
 - SATA driver
 - SMBus driver

- GeForce 169.21 drivers included (only installed if you have the hardware).


Installed and tested under Microsoft Virtual PC 2007.


Just burn to CD and enjoy.

PS: Volume License = safe to update via Windows Update. No need to deal with Windows Genuine Advantage-cracks
